<plot>Lauren Hale plays Katherine in a contemporary cult classic called "Letters from Home." The film is not readily available, so Lauren is surprised to discover at lunch one day that her server is a big fan. As her server is gushing over her, Lauren receives a phone call from a stranger inviting her to an audition at his house. Lauren wants to impress her new fan, so she accepts the invitation. Her decision to go on the audition might just change her life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?337888</url></doc>
